<p>

In the region there are three beautiful gorges for hiking. <link>
The Butterfly gorge</link> in Koutsouras, <link>
Pefki gorge</link> above the White River hamlet, and <link>
Pervolakia gorge</link> which starts from the <link>
monastery Kapsa</link>, which is one of the most impressive gorges of this area.</p>
<p>

The highest peak is <link>
Afendis Stavromenos</link> 1500 metres (4.500 feet).
The only possible way to reach the top is to walk or in a jeep 4 X 4.
